I've heard stories of people who'd been there and returned... different, weren't themselves anymore. Like Lunatics, they'd be raving about things... things I'd rather not even mention. Some had been found mutilated, but by their own hand and not someone else's. They'd have many cuts on their skin, and there'd be animal bones and various ornaments driven into their flesh.
